        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The Society must not already own a Dudhghar or Godown.\n   1. The Society must have its own land available for the construction of the Dudhghar or Godown.\n   1. The Society must not have availed of the benefit earlier under this or any other scheme for a similar purpose.\n\n",
